// Extractor pulls structured data from text
agent ContactExtractor {
    systemPrompt: "You are a contact information extractor. Extract the following from the provided text:
- name: person's full name
- email: email address
- company: organization name
- role: job title or position

let stack = [1, 2, 3]
    println("Initial stack: {stack}")

    stack.push(4)
    println("After push(4): {stack}")

    stack.push(5)
    println("After push(5): {stack}")

    let popped = stack.pop()
    println("Popped value: {popped}")
    println("After pop: {stack}")

println()
}
demoPushPop()
